brazilian bank workers were on strike 
however the national strike command said at least 75 percent of 
the bank workers joined the work stoppage 
these bank workers earn salaries ranging from 145 a month to 
about 1400 a month the banks have offered a 29 percent wage 
increase but the strikers want 81 percent 
