blast off emi usa stray cats 
 
now this is the way to do a rock n roll reunion invite a 
couple of buddies over turn the speakers up real loud and to 
steal a phrase blast off 
the stray cats pinup boys and rockabilly revivalists in the 
long ago days of president reagans first term drifted apart when 
the hits stopped coming now theyre back with blast off an 
unexpectedly delightful reunion lp that kicks snarls scratches 
and bites 
unlike most ponderous reunions where middle aged rockers check 
their lawyers at the door blast off sounds like that jam 
session with old friends where someone left a tape recorder on 
sure its more complicated than that but it doesnt sound that 
