astoundingly high a hot pink sweatshirt was offered for 78000 
zlotys about the average monthly salary 
last month poles became able to legally trade dollars for 
zlotys at about the same rate now 4000 zlotys per dollar as on 
the black market 
thus a pole with 25 perhaps sent by a relative abroad can 
turn it into 100000 zlotys 
